{"text_id":54034,"tokens":["The"," authors"," present"," an"," interesting"," approach"," to"," training"," rectified"," linear"," networks"," using"," neural"," taylor"," approximations"," (","NTA",")."," The"," NTA"," are"," used"," as"," regular","izers",","," which"," is"," similar"," but"," not"," identical"," with"," dropout"," or"," batch"," normalization",".","\n","I"," think"," that"," this"," work"," has"," some"," potential"," value"," because"," it"," may"," be"," able"," to"," improve"," performance"," on"," difficult"," tasks"," such"," as"," image"," classification"," by"," reducing"," over","fitting","."," However"," I"," have"," several"," concerns"," about"," how"," well"," their"," method"," works","."," ","\n","First"," of"," all"," they"," do"," not"," provide"," any"," experimental"," results"," showing"," improved"," accuracy"," compared"," to"," other"," methods"," like"," Dropout"," or"," Batch"," Normal","ization","."," They"," only"," show"," plots"," from"," one"," experiment"," where"," they"," compare"," different"," values"," of"," $\\","gamma","$"," -"," the"," parameter"," controlling"," the"," strength"," of"," the"," approximation"," error"," penalty"," term","."," This"," does"," not"," seem"," very"," convincing"," evidence","."," ","\n","Second",","," there"," seems"," to"," be"," no"," reason"," why"," you"," would"," want"," to"," use"," these"," approximations"," instead"," of"," standard"," dropout"," or"," batch"," normalization"," except"," perhaps"," if"," your"," network"," contains"," Re","L","Us"," at"," every"," layer"," rather"," than"," just"," input"," layers","."," It"," doesn","'","t"," make"," sense"," to"," me"," that"," you","'","d"," need"," something"," special"," when"," you","'","re"," already"," doing"," things"," like"," dropout"," anyway","..."],"sub_source":"peerread","model":"bloomz","label":1}